working index HEAD target         working index HEAD
\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-
 B       B     C    C     \-\-soft   B       B     C
                          \-\-mixed  B       C     C
                          \-\-hard   C       C     C
                          \-\-merge  C       C     C
                          \-\-keep   B       C     C
.fi
